            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ドキュメント"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Done": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dropbox · Connected": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dropbox · 接続済み"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dropbox · Connecting...": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dropbox · 接続中..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dropbox · Error": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dropbox · エラー"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dropbox · Not connected": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dropbox · 未接続"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Each rule is a regular expression tested against a photo's full Dropbox path. Capture the album name with a named group (?<name>…); the template builds the title, where ${name} inserts what that group captured. Rules are tried top to bottom and the first match wins — paths matching no rule are ignored. Tap “Insert Examples” to start, then test any path in Preview below.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "各ルールは、写真の Dropbox フルパスに対して評価される正規表現です。名前付きグループ (?<name>…) でアルバム名を取り出し、テンプレートでタイトルを作ります（${name} はそのグループが取り込んだ文字に置き換わります）。ルールは上から順に試され、最初に一致したものを採用します（どれにも一致しないパスは無視）。まず「例を挿入」を押し、下のプレビューで任意のパスを試してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Edit AI Album": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "AIアルバムを編集"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Edit Album": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "アルバムを編集"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enable folder-name albums": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フォルダー名アルバムを有効化"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enter a path to test your rules.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ルールを試すパスを入力してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Error": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "エラー"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Exclude photos already in an album": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "既にアルバムにある写真を除外"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Finding people…": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "人物を探しています…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Fine (1 row)": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "細かい（1行）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Fine (~1 km)": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "細かい（約1 km）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Folder Albums": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フォルダーアルバム"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Folder-name Albums": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フォルダー名アルバム"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Frees disk space. Cached images are re-fetched on demand, so the app stays fully functional.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ディスク容量を解放します。キャッシュ画像は必要に応じて再取得されるため、アプリは問題なく動作します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "General": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一般"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Generate Now": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今すぐ生成"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Generating…": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "生成中…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Granularity changes take effect on the next rescan.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "粒度の変更は次回の再スキャンで反映されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grid granularity": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "グリッドの粒度"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grouping": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "グルーピング"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Help": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ヘルプ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How hard the app works in the background to add CLIP embeddings (used for search). Lower is gentler on battery, network and scrolling but slower to finish; higher is faster but heavier. Takes effect on the next batch.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "検索に使う CLIP 埋め込みをバックグラウンドで付与する際の負荷の強さです。低いほど電池・通信・スクロールに優しい代わりに完了は遅く、高いほど速い代わりに重くなります。次のバッチから反映されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How rules work": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ルールの仕組み"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ignore case": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "大文字小文字を無視"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Image Recognition (AI tags)": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "画像認識（AIタグ）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Image loading for evaluation": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "評価用の画像読み込み"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "In month view, photos are packed densely and a date header appears each time this many rows fill up. Larger values show fewer headers and wider date ranges.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "月表示では写真を密に詰め、この行数ぶん埋まるたびに日付の見出しを表示します。値を大きくすると見出しが減り、日付の範囲が広くなります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Include Dropbox photos": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dropbox の写真を含める"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Infer a separate set of albums from Dropbox folder names via regex rules. Shown in the “Albums” section on the home screen.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "正規表現ルールで、Dropbox のフォルダー名から別系統のアルバムを推測します。ホーム画面の「アルバム」セクションに表示されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Infer album names from the Dropbox folder each photo lives in, using the rules below. Paths that match no rule are ignored, so junk folders (e.g. Camera Uploads) are skipped. Off by default.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "下のルールを使い、各写真がある Dropbox フォルダーからアルバム名を推測します。どのルールにも一致しないパスは無視されるため、不要なフォルダー（例：Camera Uploads）はスキップされます。既定はオフです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
